17 20-77-2905. Reimbursement for remote ultrasound procedures.
18 (a)(1) The Arkansas Medicaid Program shall reimburse for medically
19 necessary remote ultrasound procedures utilizing established Current
20 Procedural Terminology codes for remote ultrasound procedures when the
21 patient is in a residence or other off-site location from the healthcare
22 provider of the patient and the same standard of care is met.
